snippet.title: Sonic Fan Game - Chao Resort Island
snippet.description:
Chao Resort Island is a 2.5D Chao raising game available for PC and Mac!
The game takes place on a tropical island which hosts multiple resorts for you to raise your Chao in. Made by nefault1st.

Download: https://nefault1st.wordpress.com/downloads/chao-resort-island/

If you enjoyed watching this video please give us thumbs up, leave a comment below and share this video with others! Press the bell icon to get notified about new videos. It will greatly help us make more content like this.

Join our Discord server: https://dc.railgun.works/RazorAndZenon
